cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper discusses trust in conversational interactions, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC), social robots (cs.RO), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as trust is also related to security and privacy concerns. Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
